attributes.description:
2019 Fiat 500 Abarth Cabriolet manual with only 6000km!!!

Abarth, the company famous for turning Fiat's everyday models into fire-breathing sports cars, have tuned its 1.4-litre turbocharged "T-Jet" engine with 143 horse power and mated to to a five-speed manual gearbox, the feisty machine can get from a standstill to 100kph in less than 8 seconds.
Externally, the car is set apart by its sporty bumpers, 16-inch alloy wheels, and large air scoop, while the cabin gets a ''racing dashboard'' with five-inch Connect touchscreen entertainment system

This work of art comes equipped with other creature comforts such as electric sliding roof, xenon lights, cruise control, power steering, electric windows and much much more
